Package: linux-headers-maguro
Architecture: armhf
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-maguro 
Description: Linux kernel headers for the Galaxy Nexus (maguro).
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for Galaxy Nexus (maguro).

