Architecture: armhf
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-maguro
Description: Linux kernel image for the Galaxy Nexus (maguro).
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for Galaxy Nexus (maguro).

Package: linux-maguro
Architecture: armhf
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-maguro (= ${source:Version}), linux-headers-maguro (= ${source:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel for the Galaxy Nexus (maguro).
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for Galaxy Nexus (maguro).

